{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_016X8aoN5Z8Sig61GfE6ksjC","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tests pass. Here's a summary of the implementation:\n\n## Implementation Summary\n\n### `cloche resume` command\n- **Usage**: `cloche resume <run-id> [step-name]`\n- Resumes from a named step, or from the first failed step if no step is specified\n\n### Files changed\n\n**Core engine** (`internal/engine/engine.go`):\n- Added `SetPreloadedResults(map[string]string)` - configures the engine to replay stored results for completed steps instead of executing them\n\n**Prompt adapter** (`internal/adapters/agents/prompt/prompt.go`):\n- Added `ResumeConversation bool` field\n- When set: prepends `-c` flag to Claude args (resumes previous conversation) and uses `\"retry\"` as the prompt\n\n**Container runtime** (`internal/ports/container.go`, `internal/adapters/docker/runtime.go`):\n- Added `ContainerCommitter` interface with `Commit()` method\n- Added `ContainerCopier` interface with `CopyTo()` method\n- Docker implementation: `docker commit` and `docker cp`\n\n**Agent runner** (`internal/agent/runner.go`, `cmd/cloche-agent/main.go`):\n- Added `--resume-from <step>` flag to cloche-agent binary\n- Preserves `.cloche/output/` on resume (instead of cleaning it)\n- Loads completed step results from `history.log`\n- Sets `ResumeConversation` on prompt adapter for the resumed step\n\n**Host runner** (`internal/host/runner.go`, `internal/host/executor.go`):\n- Added `ResumeRun()` method - resets run state and re-executes with preloaded results\n- Added `ResumeStep` field to `Executor` for prompt conversation resume\n- Added `buildPreloadedResults()` - walks workflow graph to collect completed steps\n\n**gRPC server** (`internal/adapters/grpc/server.go`):\n- Resume is triggered via gRPC metadata on `RunWorkflow` RPC (`x-cloche-resume-run-id`, `x-cloche-resume-step`)\n- Container resume: commits container, starts new container from committed image with `--resume-from` flag\n- Host resume: delegates to `Runner.ResumeRun()`\n\n**CLI** (`cmd/cloche/main.go`, `cmd/cloche/help.go`):\n- Added `cmdResume` command\n- Added help text with usage, step-specific behavior, and examples\n\n**Domain** (`internal/domain/run.go`):\n- Added `FindFirstFailedStep()` method on `Run`\n\n### Step-specific resume behavior\n- **Script steps**: Re-executed fresh (updated scripts picked up)\n- **Prompt steps**: Conversation resumed via `-c` flag with `\"retry\"` prompt\n- **Workflow steps**: Re-executed (same as script)\n\n### Tests added\n- Engine resume tests (6 tests): linear, multi-step skip, fanout, recording, empty preload\n- Host resume tests (5 tests): `buildPreloadedResults` and `FindFirstFailedStep`\n- Prompt adapter resume test\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":159,"cache_read_input_tokens":167661,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":159},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a767d320-7441-4cfb-80d2-26edf647ec06","uuid":"4614b165-2449-4671-b090-5830c11effab"}
